Installation instructions libnetmeter
-------------------------------------

Prerequisites
-------------
Linux or Unix compatible operating system
- cmake version 2.4 or higher (patch 5 recommended)
Development packages of:
 - libxml2
 - libxslt

Archive extraction
------------------
Probably you already did this

$ tar -xzvf libnetmeter-$VERSION.tar.gz

Where $VERSION is the package version

Compilation and Installation
----------------------------
To compile and install libnetmeter using cmake run:
$ cd libnetmeter-$VERSION
$ ./configure.cmake --prefix=<netmeter_library_path>
$ cmake .
$ make
$ [sudo] make install

Where <netmeter_library_path> is the installation directory.
If none specified the system uses /usr/local/netmeter

